Key Observation: after sorting, if there is a solution, one of them must be a continuous segment of the weights.

Reason: for each n, the number of elements chosen, it is >= first n, <= last n added together, then we can start from the fromer, remove first chosen and append the next one until we reach the latter. 

[l1, r1]
[l2, r2]
[l3, r3]
...
[ln-1, rn-1]
[ln, rn]